{"parentUuid":"94695d32-c0bf-4164-a637-084b324c43d5","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"c8e03966-bce7-4e19-8921-113557d74d75","version":"2.1.50","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"cozy-marinating-galaxy","type":"progress","data":{"message":{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01YMpsbLcyqzDqA9WgrZkbYV","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Vortice.Windows DXGI Desktop Duplication example C# screen capture 2025\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Desktop Duplication Sample · Issue #42 · amerkoleci/Vortice.Windows\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/amerkoleci/Vortice.Windows/issues/42\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - GERD0GDU/dxgi_desktop_capture: Project that captures the desktop image with DXGI duplication. Saves the captured image to the file in different image formats (*.bmp; *.jpg; *.tif).\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/GERD0GDU/dxgi_desktop_capture\"},{\"title\":\"Desktop Duplication API - Win32 apps | Microsoft Learn\",\"url\":\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/direct3ddxgi/desktop-dup-api\"},{\"title\":\"C++ screenshot using DXGI DuplicateOutput of screen is missing Game Bar drawn areas - Microsoft Q&A\",\"url\":\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-sg/answers/questions/1615485/c-screenshot-using-dxgi-duplicateoutput-of-screen\"},{\"title\":\"Desktop Screen Capture on Windows via Windows Desktop Duplication API with Drawing of Cursor's Image- CodeProject\",\"url\":\"https://www.codeproject.com/Tips/1116253/Desktop-Screen-Capture-on-Windows-via-Windows-Desk\"},{\"title\":\"Windows Graphics Capture vs DXGI Desktop Duplication | OBS Forums\",\"url\":\"https://obsproject.com/forum/threads/windows-graphics-capture-vs-dxgi-desktop-duplication.149320/\"},{\"title\":\"Simon Mourier's Blog - dxgi\",\"url\":\"https://www.simonmourier.com/Blog/Category/dxgi\"},{\"title\":\"NuGet Gallery | Vortice.DXGI 3.8.2\",\"url\":\"https://www.nuget.org/packages/Vortice.DXGI\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - amerkoleci/Vortice.Windows: .NET bindings for Direct3D12, Direct3D11, WIC, Direct2D1, XInput, XAudio, X3DAudio, DXC, Direct3D9 and DirectInput.\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/amerkoleci/Vortice.Windows\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - Shehryar/Duplicator: Screen Capture and Video Recording C# samples\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/Shehryar/Duplicator\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, I found relevant information about Vortice.Windows and DXGI Desktop Duplication:\n\n## Vortice.Windows Overview\n\nVortice.Windows is a collection of Win32 and UWP libraries with bindings support for DXGI, WIC, DirectWrite, Direct2D, Direct3D9, Direct3D11, Direct3D12, XInput, XAudio2, X3DAudio, DirectInput, DirectStorage, DirectML, UIAnimation and DirectSound. This library targets .net9.0 and .net10.0 and uses modern C#.\n\n## Sample Resources\n\nThere is a collection of samples available in Vortice.Windows.Samples. You can find these samples on the [Vortice.Windows GitHub repository](https://github.com/amerkoleci/Vortice.Windows).\n\nAdditionally, Vortice.Windows includes bindings support for DXGI, WIC, DirectWrite, Direct2D, Direct3D9, Direct3D11, Direct3D12, XInput, XAudio2, X3DAudio, DirectInput, DirectStorage, DirectML, UIAnimation and DirectSound.\n\nFor practical C# examples of screen capture using Desktop Duplication, you might also want to look at the [Vortice.Windows.Samples repository](https://github.com/amerkoleci/Vortice.Windows.Samples) for specific desktop duplication examples. The library provides modern C# bindings for the underlying DXGI APIs needed for screen capture functionality.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"eedb940c-d375-4a54-9c2b-5e395b7b8723","timestamp":"2026-02-21T11:59:43.368Z"},"normalizedMessages":[],"type":"agent_progress","prompt":"Phase 1 MVP 설계를 해줘. 커스텀 원격 데스크톱 솔루션의 LAN 화면 공유 MVP.\n\n## 배경\n- 설비 PC에 원격 접속하여 화면 공유/제어하는 솔루션\n- TeamViewer/AnyDesk 대체 자체 솔루션\n- MCP/AI Agent 기능은 현재 범위에서 제외\n\n## 확정 사항\n- C# .NET 8 (LTS)\n- Agent: 트레이 앱 (Windows Service 아님 — DXGI가 Session 0에서 안 됨)\n- Client: WinForms\n- DXGI Desktop Duplication API로 화면 캡처\n- Win32 SendInput으로 입력 시뮬레이션\n- Raw TCP + 커스텀 프로토콜 (VNC/RFB 아님)\n- JPEG 압축\n- LAN 기본 FPS: 15\n- 인증: 챌린지-리스펀스 (nonce + SHA256)\n- 프로젝트 경로: C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\DAEHYUN_PRIVATE\\RemoteControl\n\n## 프로젝트 구조 (Phase 1 범위)\n- RemoteDesktop.Common — 공통 프로토콜, 모델, 직렬화\n- RemoteDesktop.Agent — 설비 PC 트레이 앱 (화면 캡처 + TCP 리스너 + 입력 시뮬)\n- RemoteDesktop.Client — WinForms 뷰어 (원격 화면 표시 + 마우스/키보드 전송)\n\n## 패킷 구조\n[4 byte 패킷 길이] + [1 byte 패킷 타입] + [N byte 페이로드]\n\n## Phase 1 패킷 (MVP)\n| 코드 | 패킷명 | 방향 | 설명 |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 0x01 | AUTH_REQUEST | Client → Agent | 접속 인증 요청 |\n| 0x02 | AUTH_RESPONSE | Agent → Client | 인증 결과 |\n| 0x03 | AUTH_CHALLENGE | Agent → Client | 챌린지 nonce 전송 |\n| 0x10 | SCREEN_FULL | Agent → Client | 전체 화면 프레임 (JPEG) |\n| 0x20 | MOUSE_MOVE | Client → Agent | 마우스 이동 |\n| 0x21 | MOUSE_CLICK | Client → Agent | 마우스 클릭 |\n| 0x22 | MOUSE_SCROLL | Client → Agent | 마우스 스크롤 |\n| 0x30 | KEY_EVENT | Client → Agent | 키보드 입력 |\n| 0xF0 | HEARTBEAT | 양방향 | 연결 유지 (5초) |\n\n## 설계 요청\n다음을 포함한 상세 구현 계획을 만들어줘:\n\n1. **솔루션 구조**: 프로젝트별 폴더/파일 구조\n2. **Common 라이브러리**: 패킷 정의, 직렬화/역직렬화, TCP 헬퍼\n3. **Agent 아키텍처**: \n   - DXGI Desktop Duplication 화면 캡처 (15fps 타이머)\n   - TCP 리스너 (포트 5900)\n   - 인증 처리 (챌린지-리스펀스)\n   - JPEG 인코딩\n   - SendInput 입력 시뮬레이션\n   - 트레이 앱 구조 (NotifyIcon)\n4. **Client 아키텍처**:\n   - 접속 폼 (IP/비밀번호 입력)\n   - 뷰어 폼 (PictureBox or Panel + 더블버퍼링)\n   - 마우스/키보드 이벤트 캡처 및 전송\n   - 화면 비율 맞춤 (스케일링)\n\n각 파일의 주요 클래스/메서드 시그니처까지 포함해줘. 구현 순서도 제시해줘.\n","agentId":"a310437eca56b979c"},"toolUseID":"agent_msg_01VJQGDdge9eLuUbopGXRjpY","parentToolUseID":"toolu_01MGohPE7wp5TVS4dLtXj5ua","uuid":"18f4e463-01e3-4c77-8849-3bfe26475fc3","timestamp":"2026-02-21T11:59:43.370Z"}
{"parentUuid":"18f4e463-01e3-4c77-8849-3bfe26475fc3","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"c8e03966-bce7-4e19-8921-113557d74d75","version":"2.1.50","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"cozy-marinating-galaxy","type":"progress","data":{"message":{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01XYab1BBufQLTEAbtNojwEc","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"C# .NET 8 WinForms NotifyIcon system tray application template\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Add Application Icons to the TaskBar with NotifyIcon Component - Windows Forms | Microsoft Learn\",\"url\":\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/desktop/winforms/controls/app-icons-to-the-taskbar-with-wf-notifyicon\"},{\"title\":\"Lightweight System Tray Application (NotifyIcon Based) | Mitchel Sellers\",\"url\":\"https://mitchelsellers.com/blog/article/lightweight-system-tray-application-notifyicon-based\"},{\"title\":\"Creating Tray Applications in .NET: A Practical Guide | Simple Talk\",\"url\":\"https://www.red-gate.com/simple-talk/development/dotnet-development/creating-tray-applications-in-net-a-practical-guide/\"},{\"title\":\"Add a Notify Icon to the System Tray with C#\",\"url\":\"https://www.daveoncsharp.com/2009/08/add-notify-icon-to-system-tray/\"},{\"title\":\"Use of Notification Tray Icons in .NET 8.0 in WPF\",\"url\":\"https://www.c-sharpcorner.com/blogs/use-of-notification-tray-icons-in-net-80-in-wpf\"},{\"title\":\"Implementing a System Tray App with WPF and MVVM - RoundWide Systems\",\"url\":\"https://roundwide.com/implementing-system-tray-app-with-wpf-and-mvvm/\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - kesac/SystemTrayApp: Example of a basic system tray app using .NET Windows Forms\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/kesac/SystemTrayApp\"},{\"title\":\"NotifyIcon Class (System.Windows.Forms) | Microsoft Learn\",\"url\":\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/system.windows.forms.notifyicon?view=windowsdesktop-8.0\"},{\"title\":\"Notify Icon In C#\",\"url\":\"https://www.c-sharpcorner.com/UploadFile/mahesh/notify-icon-in-C-Sharp/\"},{\"title\":\"How to Create a System tray Notification in C#\",\"url\":\"https://foxlearn.com/windows-forms/how-to-create-a-system-tray-notification-in-csharp-283.html\"}]\n\nI found comprehensive information about creating C# .NET WinForms NotifyIcon system tray applications. Here are the key findings from the search results:\n\n## Key Resources\n\n**Official Microsoft Documentation:**\nThe Windows Forms NotifyIcon component displays a single icon in the status notification area of the taskbar. Microsoft Learn provides official guidance on implementing NotifyIcon components with detailed code examples.\n\n## Basic Implementation Approaches\n\n**1. Form-Centric Approach:**\nTo start off create a C# Windows Forms Application project and on your main form drag the NotifyIcon component from the toolbox to the form. From the component's properties you can set the icon to be displayed in the system tray, the text to be displayed when the mouse hovers over the tray icon, balloon tip settings, and other common properties that most of the .NET components have.\n\n**2. ApplicationContext Approach:**\nThe method involves creating a new ApplicationContext object and declaring the NotifyIcon and ContextMenu in the code for the application context. An application context object can be used by the \"Application.Run()\" method to actually run the application.\n\n## Essential Components\n\nDrag and drop a NotifyIcon, ContextMenuStrip controls from the toolbox onto your form. The Icon property sets the icon that will appear in the systray for this application. The ContextMenu property sets the menu that will appear when the systray icon is right clicked.\n\n## Practical Example Repository\n\nThere's an example of a basic system tray app using .NET Windows Forms available on GitHub (kesac/SystemTrayApp).\n\nThe Microsoft Learn documentation on NotifyIcon (version 8.0) and the Simple Talk article \"Creating Tray Applications in .NET: A Practical Guide\" are excellent resources for comprehensive implementation details specific to .NET 8.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"e9659aa8-b792-4979-aa00-a99437ce6887","timestamp":"2026-02-21T11:59:46.299Z"},"normalizedMessages":[],"type":"agent_progress","prompt":"Phase 1 MVP 설계를 해줘. 커스텀 원격 데스크톱 솔루션의 LAN 화면 공유 MVP.\n\n## 배경\n- 설비 PC에 원격 접속하여 화면 공유/제어하는 솔루션\n- TeamViewer/AnyDesk 대체 자체 솔루션\n- MCP/AI Agent 기능은 현재 범위에서 제외\n\n## 확정 사항\n- C# .NET 8 (LTS)\n- Agent: 트레이 앱 (Windows Service 아님 — DXGI가 Session 0에서 안 됨)\n- Client: WinForms\n- DXGI Desktop Duplication API로 화면 캡처\n- Win32 SendInput으로 입력 시뮬레이션\n- Raw TCP + 커스텀 프로토콜 (VNC/RFB 아님)\n- JPEG 압축\n- LAN 기본 FPS: 15\n- 인증: 챌린지-리스펀스 (nonce + SHA256)\n- 프로젝트 경로: C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\DAEHYUN_PRIVATE\\RemoteControl\n\n## 프로젝트 구조 (Phase 1 범위)\n- RemoteDesktop.Common — 공통 프로토콜, 모델, 직렬화\n- RemoteDesktop.Agent — 설비 PC 트레이 앱 (화면 캡처 + TCP 리스너 + 입력 시뮬)\n- RemoteDesktop.Client — WinForms 뷰어 (원격 화면 표시 + 마우스/키보드 전송)\n\n## 패킷 구조\n[4 byte 패킷 길이] + [1 byte 패킷 타입] + [N byte 페이로드]\n\n## Phase 1 패킷 (MVP)\n| 코드 | 패킷명 | 방향 | 설명 |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 0x01 | AUTH_REQUEST | Client → Agent | 접속 인증 요청 |\n| 0x02 | AUTH_RESPONSE | Agent → Client | 인증 결과 |\n| 0x03 | AUTH_CHALLENGE | Agent → Client | 챌린지 nonce 전송 |\n| 0x10 | SCREEN_FULL | Agent → Client | 전체 화면 프레임 (JPEG) |\n| 0x20 | MOUSE_MOVE | Client → Agent | 마우스 이동 |\n| 0x21 | MOUSE_CLICK | Client → Agent | 마우스 클릭 |\n| 0x22 | MOUSE_SCROLL | Client → Agent | 마우스 스크롤 |\n| 0x30 | KEY_EVENT | Client → Agent | 키보드 입력 |\n| 0xF0 | HEARTBEAT | 양방향 | 연결 유지 (5초) |\n\n## 설계 요청\n다음을 포함한 상세 구현 계획을 만들어줘:\n\n1. **솔루션 구조**: 프로젝트별 폴더/파일 구조\n2. **Common 라이브러리**: 패킷 정의, 직렬화/역직렬화, TCP 헬퍼\n3. **Agent 아키텍처**: \n   - DXGI Desktop Duplication 화면 캡처 (15fps 타이머)\n   - TCP 리스너 (포트 5900)\n   - 인증 처리 (챌린지-리스펀스)\n   - JPEG 인코딩\n   - SendInput 입력 시뮬레이션\n   - 트레이 앱 구조 (NotifyIcon)\n4. **Client 아키텍처**:\n   - 접속 폼 (IP/비밀번호 입력)\n   - 뷰어 폼 (PictureBox or Panel + 더블버퍼링)\n   - 마우스/키보드 이벤트 캡처 및 전송\n   - 화면 비율 맞춤 (스케일링)\n\n각 파일의 주요 클래스/메서드 시그니처까지 포함해줘. 구현 순서도 제시해줘.\n","agentId":"a310437eca56b979c"},"toolUseID":"agent_msg_01VJQGDdge9eLuUbopGXRjpY","parentToolUseID":"toolu_01MGohPE7wp5TVS4dLtXj5ua","uuid":"e492e0a0-5f0c-45e9-af52-a56204aee5a2","timestamp":"2026-02-21T11:59:46.300Z"}
{"parentUuid":"e492e0a0-5f0c-45e9-af52-a56204aee5a2","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"c8e03966-bce7-4e19-8921-113557d74d75","version":"2.1.50","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"cozy-marinating-galaxy","type":"progress","data":{"message":{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01NeDNQ96KB8Nj2yqyoDygTS","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"C# challenge response authentication nonce SHA256 implementation\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Salted Challenge Response Authentication Mechanism (SCRAM) SHA-1 - CodeProject\",\"url\":\"https://www.codeproject.com/Articles/698219/Salted-Challenge-Response-Authentication-Mechanism\"},{\"title\":\"Challenge–response authentication - Wikipedia\",\"url\":\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Challenge%E2%80%93response_authentication\"},{\"title\":\"cs468-challenge-response-authentication/RShellClient2.c at master · sergiomdl77/cs468-challenge-response-authentication\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/sergiomdl77/cs468-challenge-response-authentication/blob/master/RShellClient2.c\"},{\"title\":\"Implementing Digest Authentication in .NET\",\"url\":\"https://callumhoughton18.github.io/Personal-Site/blog/digest-auth-in-dotnet/\"},{\"title\":\"HMAC Authentication in Web API - Dot Net Tutorials\",\"url\":\"https://dotnettutorials.net/lesson/hmac-authentication-web-api/\"},{\"title\":\"Salted Challenge Response Authentication Mechanism - Wikipedia\",\"url\":\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Salted_Challenge_Response_Authentication_Mechanism\"},{\"title\":\"Challenge-response authentication\",\"url\":\"https://assets.ctfassets.net/yd8ev1715agv/6FyCzYLiNk9hXrPR76aULd/f21f9991f26166d26d4aa59b1373f6b9/Faktaark_innlogging_App-ID.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"Demystifying OpenID Connect's State & Nonce Parameters in ASP.NET Core\",\"url\":\"https://nestenius.se/net/demystifying-openid-connects-state-and-nonce-parameters-in-asp-net-core/\"},{\"title\":\"ASP.NET Core using Proof Key for Code Exchange (PKCE)\",\"url\":\"https://www.scottbrady.io/openid-connect/aspnet-core-using-proof-key-for-code-exchange-pkce\"},{\"title\":\"Salted Challenge Response Authentication Mechanism (SCRAM)\",\"url\":\"https://www.1kosmos.com/security-glossary/salted-challenge-response-authentication-mechanism-scram/\"}]\n\nI've found comprehensive information on C# challenge-response authentication with nonce and SHA256. Here are the key results:\n\n## SCRAM Authentication Implementation\n\nA C# implementation of the SCRAM SHA-1 (RFC 5802) authentication protocol is available on CodeProject. The implementation covers the core components:\n\n- The implementation sets the default length of the client nonce to 32 bytes, and increasing the length of this nonce helps increase difficulty for off-line dictionary attacks\n- The client nonce is a value randomly generated by the client ideally using a cryptographic random generator, and must be different for each authentication session\n- The server nonce is similar to the client nonce and must be different for each authentication session and be cryptographically secure\n\n## HMAC Authentication with SHA256\n\nThe client generates a HASH using SHA256 of a combined parameter string, using the Private Secret API Key provided by the server. The nonce and timestamp values are included in creating the request signature as well as sent as plain text values to protect the API from replay attacks.\n\n## General Challenge-Response Principles\n\nAuthentication protocols usually employ a cryptographic nonce as the challenge to ensure every challenge–response sequence is unique, which protects against eavesdropping with subsequent replay attacks.\n\nThe CodeProject article provides working code examples implementing SCRAM-SHA1 for C# developers who need a complete authentication mechanism with nonce support.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"940bfb63-0953-4d70-8e55-60a34ba1312c","timestamp":"2026-02-21T11:59:48.463Z"},"normalizedMessages":[],"type":"agent_progress","prompt":"Phase 1 MVP 설계를 해줘. 커스텀 원격 데스크톱 솔루션의 LAN 화면 공유 MVP.\n\n## 배경\n- 설비 PC에 원격 접속하여 화면 공유/제어하는 솔루션\n- TeamViewer/AnyDesk 대체 자체 솔루션\n- MCP/AI Agent 기능은 현재 범위에서 제외\n\n## 확정 사항\n- C# .NET 8 (LTS)\n- Agent: 트레이 앱 (Windows Service 아님 — DXGI가 Session 0에서 안 됨)\n- Client: WinForms\n- DXGI Desktop Duplication API로 화면 캡처\n- Win32 SendInput으로 입력 시뮬레이션\n- Raw TCP + 커스텀 프로토콜 (VNC/RFB 아님)\n- JPEG 압축\n- LAN 기본 FPS: 15\n- 인증: 챌린지-리스펀스 (nonce + SHA256)\n- 프로젝트 경로: C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\DAEHYUN_PRIVATE\\RemoteControl\n\n## 프로젝트 구조 (Phase 1 범위)\n- RemoteDesktop.Common — 공통 프로토콜, 모델, 직렬화\n- RemoteDesktop.Agent — 설비 PC 트레이 앱 (화면 캡처 + TCP 리스너 + 입력 시뮬)\n- RemoteDesktop.Client — WinForms 뷰어 (원격 화면 표시 + 마우스/키보드 전송)\n\n## 패킷 구조\n[4 byte 패킷 길이] + [1 byte 패킷 타입] + [N byte 페이로드]\n\n## Phase 1 패킷 (MVP)\n| 코드 | 패킷명 | 방향 | 설명 |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 0x01 | AUTH_REQUEST | Client → Agent | 접속 인증 요청 |\n| 0x02 | AUTH_RESPONSE | Agent → Client | 인증 결과 |\n| 0x03 | AUTH_CHALLENGE | Agent → Client | 챌린지 nonce 전송 |\n| 0x10 | SCREEN_FULL | Agent → Client | 전체 화면 프레임 (JPEG) |\n| 0x20 | MOUSE_MOVE | Client → Agent | 마우스 이동 |\n| 0x21 | MOUSE_CLICK | Client → Agent | 마우스 클릭 |\n| 0x22 | MOUSE_SCROLL | Client → Agent | 마우스 스크롤 |\n| 0x30 | KEY_EVENT | Client → Agent | 키보드 입력 |\n| 0xF0 | HEARTBEAT | 양방향 | 연결 유지 (5초) |\n\n## 설계 요청\n다음을 포함한 상세 구현 계획을 만들어줘:\n\n1. **솔루션 구조**: 프로젝트별 폴더/파일 구조\n2. **Common 라이브러리**: 패킷 정의, 직렬화/역직렬화, TCP 헬퍼\n3. **Agent 아키텍처**: \n   - DXGI Desktop Duplication 화면 캡처 (15fps 타이머)\n   - TCP 리스너 (포트 5900)\n   - 인증 처리 (챌린지-리스펀스)\n   - JPEG 인코딩\n   - SendInput 입력 시뮬레이션\n   - 트레이 앱 구조 (NotifyIcon)\n4. **Client 아키텍처**:\n   - 접속 폼 (IP/비밀번호 입력)\n   - 뷰어 폼 (PictureBox or Panel + 더블버퍼링)\n   - 마우스/키보드 이벤트 캡처 및 전송\n   - 화면 비율 맞춤 (스케일링)\n\n각 파일의 주요 클래스/메서드 시그니처까지 포함해줘. 구현 순서도 제시해줘.\n","agentId":"a310437eca56b979c"},"toolUseID":"agent_msg_01VJQGDdge9eLuUbopGXRjpY","parentToolUseID":"toolu_01MGohPE7wp5TVS4dLtXj5ua","uuid":"5c4b4f12-66ca-4556-ade7-c6d5b09e28d4","timestamp":"2026-02-21T11:59:48.465Z"}
