{"parentUuid":"7d500a13-df92-46d4-a526-3fb1729b859d","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"c8e03966-bce7-4e19-8921-113557d74d75","version":"2.1.50","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"cozy-marinating-galaxy","type":"progress","data":{"message":{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019aEz4nrJjwkVTwMcpPnqsY","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Vortice.Windows nuget .NET 8 compatibility target framework 2024 2025\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Target frameworks in SDK-style projects - .NET | Microsoft Learn\",\"url\":\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/standard/frameworks\"},{\"title\":\"NuGet Gallery | Vortice.WinForms 3.7.5-beta\",\"url\":\"https://www.nuget.org/packages/Vortice.WinForms/3.7.5-beta\"},{\"title\":\"NuGet Gallery | Vortice.DirectX 3.8.2\",\"url\":\"https://www.nuget.org/packages/Vortice.DirectX/\"},{\"title\":\"NuGet Gallery | Vortice.D3DCompiler 3.7.1-beta\",\"url\":\"https://nugetprodusnc.azure-api.net/packages/Vortice.D3DCompiler/3.7.1-beta\"},{\"title\":\"NuGet Gallery | Vortice.Win32 2.3.0\",\"url\":\"https://www.nuget.org/packages/Vortice.Win32\"},{\"title\":\"NuGet Gallery | Vortice.DXGI 3.8.2\",\"url\":\"https://www.nuget.org/packages/Vortice.DXGI\"},{\"title\":\"NuGet Gallery | Vortice.XInput 3.6.2\",\"url\":\"https://www.nuget.org/packages/Vortice.XInput/\"},{\"title\":\"NuGet Gallery | Vortice.Mathematics 2.1.0\",\"url\":\"https://www.nuget.org/packages/Vortice.Mathematics\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - amerkoleci/Vortice.Windows: .NET bindings for Direct3D12, Direct3D11, WIC, Direct2D1, XInput, XAudio, X3DAudio, DXC, Direct3D9 and DirectInput.\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/amerkoleci/Vortice.Windows\"},{\"title\":\"NuGet Gallery | Vortice.DirectStorage 3.8.2\",\"url\":\"https://www.nuget.org/packages/Vortice.DirectStorage/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found regarding Vortice.Windows NuGet packages and .NET 8 compatibility:\n\n## Target Framework Support\n\nThe Vortice.Windows ecosystem has varying target framework support depending on the specific package:\n\n**Older packages** (2024 releases):\n- Vortice.WinForms targets .NET 8.0 and .NET 9.0\n- Vortice.D3DCompiler (3.7.1-beta) targets .NET 8.0 and .NET 9.0\n- Vortice.XInput (3.6.2) targets .NET 8.0 and is compatible with this framework or higher\n\n**Newer packages** (2025 releases):\n- Vortice.DirectX (3.8.2) targets .NET 9.0 and .NET 10.0\n- Vortice.DXGI (3.8.2) targets .NET 9.0 and .NET 10.0\n- The main Vortice.Windows library targets .NET 9.0 and .NET 10.0\n\n**Cross-platform math library**:\n- Vortice.Mathematics is a high-performance cross platform .NET 8, .NET 9 and .NET 10 math library\n\nIt appears that newer versions of Vortice.Windows packages have dropped .NET 8.0 support in favor of .NET 9.0 and .NET 10.0 in 2025, though some older packages still maintain .NET 8.0 compatibility.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"7d44399b-3234-49c1-8151-84ce3ee01648","timestamp":"2026-02-21T11:59:58.433Z"},"normalizedMessages":[],"type":"agent_progress","prompt":"Phase 1 MVP 설계를 해줘. 커스텀 원격 데스크톱 솔루션의 LAN 화면 공유 MVP.\n\n## 배경\n- 설비 PC에 원격 접속하여 화면 공유/제어하는 솔루션\n- TeamViewer/AnyDesk 대체 자체 솔루션\n- MCP/AI Agent 기능은 현재 범위에서 제외\n\n## 확정 사항\n- C# .NET 8 (LTS)\n- Agent: 트레이 앱 (Windows Service 아님 — DXGI가 Session 0에서 안 됨)\n- Client: WinForms\n- DXGI Desktop Duplication API로 화면 캡처\n- Win32 SendInput으로 입력 시뮬레이션\n- Raw TCP + 커스텀 프로토콜 (VNC/RFB 아님)\n- JPEG 압축\n- LAN 기본 FPS: 15\n- 인증: 챌린지-리스펀스 (nonce + SHA256)\n- 프로젝트 경로: C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop\\DAEHYUN_PRIVATE\\RemoteControl\n\n## 프로젝트 구조 (Phase 1 범위)\n- RemoteDesktop.Common — 공통 프로토콜, 모델, 직렬화\n- RemoteDesktop.Agent — 설비 PC 트레이 앱 (화면 캡처 + TCP 리스너 + 입력 시뮬)\n- RemoteDesktop.Client — WinForms 뷰어 (원격 화면 표시 + 마우스/키보드 전송)\n\n## 패킷 구조\n[4 byte 패킷 길이] + [1 byte 패킷 타입] + [N byte 페이로드]\n\n## Phase 1 패킷 (MVP)\n| 코드 | 패킷명 | 방향 | 설명 |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 0x01 | AUTH_REQUEST | Client → Agent | 접속 인증 요청 |\n| 0x02 | AUTH_RESPONSE | Agent → Client | 인증 결과 |\n| 0x03 | AUTH_CHALLENGE | Agent → Client | 챌린지 nonce 전송 |\n| 0x10 | SCREEN_FULL | Agent → Client | 전체 화면 프레임 (JPEG) |\n| 0x20 | MOUSE_MOVE | Client → Agent | 마우스 이동 |\n| 0x21 | MOUSE_CLICK | Client → Agent | 마우스 클릭 |\n| 0x22 | MOUSE_SCROLL | Client → Agent | 마우스 스크롤 |\n| 0x30 | KEY_EVENT | Client → Agent | 키보드 입력 |\n| 0xF0 | HEARTBEAT | 양방향 | 연결 유지 (5초) |\n\n## 설계 요청\n다음을 포함한 상세 구현 계획을 만들어줘:\n\n1. **솔루션 구조**: 프로젝트별 폴더/파일 구조\n2. **Common 라이브러리**: 패킷 정의, 직렬화/역직렬화, TCP 헬퍼\n3. **Agent 아키텍처**: \n   - DXGI Desktop Duplication 화면 캡처 (15fps 타이머)\n   - TCP 리스너 (포트 5900)\n   - 인증 처리 (챌린지-리스펀스)\n   - JPEG 인코딩\n   - SendInput 입력 시뮬레이션\n   - 트레이 앱 구조 (NotifyIcon)\n4. **Client 아키텍처**:\n   - 접속 폼 (IP/비밀번호 입력)\n   - 뷰어 폼 (PictureBox or Panel + 더블버퍼링)\n   - 마우스/키보드 이벤트 캡처 및 전송\n   - 화면 비율 맞춤 (스케일링)\n\n각 파일의 주요 클래스/메서드 시그니처까지 포함해줘. 구현 순서도 제시해줘.\n","agentId":"a310437eca56b979c"},"toolUseID":"agent_msg_01VJQGDdge9eLuUbopGXRjpY","parentToolUseID":"toolu_01MGohPE7wp5TVS4dLtXj5ua","uuid":"1fee1cdd-0c81-4b93-bed0-051ef90b5041","timestamp":"2026-02-21T11:59:58.434Z"}
{"parentUuid":"1fee1cdd-0c81-4b93-bed0-051ef90b5041","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"c8e03966-bce7-4e19-8921-113557d74d75","version":"2.1.50","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"cozy-marinating-galaxy","type":"progress","data":{"message":{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SRRbPPN2xWvEkYwZxhmAbQ","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"C# DXGI Desktop Duplication raw COM interop without SharpDX Vortice P/Invoke .NET 8\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Desktop Duplication Sample · Issue #42 · amerkoleci/Vortice.Windows\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/amerkoleci/Vortice.Windows/issues/42\"},{\"title\":\"Desktop Duplication API - Win32 apps | Microsoft Learn\",\"url\":\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/direct3ddxgi/desktop-dup-api\"},{\"title\":\"desktop-duplication-net/DesktopDuplication/DesktopDuplicator.cs at master · jasonpang/desktop-duplication-net\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/jasonpang/desktop-duplication-net/blob/master/DesktopDuplication/DesktopDuplicator.cs\"},{\"title\":\"Simon Mourier's Blog - dxgi\",\"url\":\"https://www.simonmourier.com/Blog/Category/dxgi\"},{\"title\":\"DirectX and COM interoperability for .NET · microsoft/CsWin32 · Discussion #705\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/microsoft/CsWin32/discussions/705\"},{\"title\":\"Desktop Duplication - Windows drivers | Microsoft Learn\",\"url\":\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-hardware/drivers/display/desktop-duplication-api\"},{\"title\":\"NuGet Gallery | DesktopDuplication 1.0.1\",\"url\":\"https://www.nuget.org/packages/DesktopDuplication\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - jasonpang/desktop-duplication-net: Windows 8 Desktop Duplication API for C# and .NET.\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/jasonpang/desktop-duplication-net\"},{\"title\":\"DXGI desktop duplication sample\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/microsoft/Windows-classic-samples/blob/main/Samples/DXGIDesktopDuplication/README.md\"},{\"title\":\"SlimdDX or Microsoft Managed DirectX - Engines and Middleware - GameDev.net\",\"url\":\"https://www.gamedev.net/forums/topic/712629-slimddx-or-microsoft-managed-directx/\"}]\n\nI found several relevant resources for working with C# DXGI Desktop Duplication using raw COM interop without SharpDX:\n\n## Key Resources\n\n1. **Microsoft Official Documentation**: Windows 8 disables standard Windows 2000 Display Driver Model (XDDM) mirror drivers and offers the desktop duplication API instead, which provides remote access to a desktop image for collaboration scenarios and allows apps to access frame-by-frame updates to the desktop.\n\n2. **GitHub Projects**:\n   - **jasonpang/desktop-duplication-net**: A Windows 8 Desktop Duplication API implementation for C# and .NET (found at https://github.com/jasonpang/desktop-duplication-net)\n   - **Microsoft Windows Classic Samples**: A sample that demonstrates how to use the desktop duplication behaviors exposed by DXGI in DirectX, written in C++ (provides reference implementations)\n\n3. **Alternative Libraries**: For lower-level COM interop alternatives to SharpDX, you can consider TerraFX (which provides low-level interop bindings for Windows closer to C++ examples) or Vortice, both available as NuGet packages and regularly updated.\n\n4. **CsWin32 Project**: CsWin32 has been used successfully for simple DXGI tests including enumerating adapters and outputs (https://github.com/microsoft/CsWin32), which provides generated COM interop for modern .NET.\n\nThe official Microsoft Learn documentation at https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/direct3ddxgi/desktop-dup-api contains the canonical API specifications you'll need for raw P/Invoke implementations in .NET 8.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"f04bc33a-f651-48ab-81ed-b871b7b92ff6","timestamp":"2026-02-21T12:00:01.343Z"},"normalizedMessages":[],"type":"agent_progress","prompt"